Warning:
The European drug checking group that analyzed this sample issued a warning because it contains a drug other than the one it was represented as.

See original Energy Control alert on fake alprazolam tablets and powder for more details.

*Republished from the Energy Control alert:

'Four [samples] from three different users have been received from 13/Nov/18 to 15/Jan/19 ( 3 from US, 1 from Hong Kong). These samples were submitted as alprazolam in powder and drug checking revealed the mentioned results with additional 3-6 unidentified molecules.

Test result of another powder sample submitted as alprazolam and received from Portugal on 28/Jan/18 reveals the presence of this combination (promethazine. cyproheptadine and amantadine + 2 unidentified substances) with the addition of chlorpheniramine.'
